{"type": "article", "id": 54063, "title": "一个新设计品牌，想要赋予新家具老物件的味道｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-06-07T23:25:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 50936, "name": "SITIA"}, {"id": 1330, "name": "ASOS"}, {"id": 40435, "name": "Crayola"}, {"id": 50937, "name": "Christopher Sarkisian"}, {"id": 50938, "name": "Elena Trevisan"}, {"id": 50939, "name": "Parisa Katouzian"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 190, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180607213512a6sjlxAnEFgSyfwJ.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Revised Collection by Suzy and Casper Vissers</h3><p>当我们不再满意于生活现状以及周围环境时，某个时间点就会开始进行自我反思。设计师Sjoerd Vroonland、Suzy 和 Casper Vissers 三年前意识到这一点时，开始尝试创造一个名为 REVISED 的设计品牌，灵感就是源自那个自我反思的关键时刻。</p><p>Revised 系列包括椅子、桌子、收纳产品、灯饰和家居饰品，设计团队希望每件作品都能穿搭出舒适、温暖、极具亲和力的味道，即便是全新的额家具和装饰品，也像是老辈人留下来的传家宝一样。整个系列的特点都是简单的线条、柔和的曲线和纤细的轮廓，融合了木材、大理石、金属和玻璃等材质。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213608vmtdySof1Tnbe85g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.479769\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213608h7JApQmWcSG15Es4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213608uCWadA6YONh5wFoV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.425390\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213608Vm9hN1Gzl3eU2Epu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213609SI5VxT4fQUEWiotz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213609jvGKu7yHzkPqefYA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213609tdKUSRJrXN243AxV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213609RUgz6sPipbOMLfFm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.919604\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://revised.com/collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">REVISED</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Pot Hob by Parisa Katouzian</h3><p>很多人做饭都有个习惯，在燃气灶上烹饪食物用一种锅具，端上桌前会换上一个外观更精致的餐盘。设计师 Parisa Katouzian 由此产生了一个疑问：为什么烹饪的锅具不够有吸引力？为此她设计了名为 Pot Hob 的锅具套装，包括煎锅、水壶、汤锅和平底锅，既是烹饪容器，也可以当作优雅的餐盘。</p><p>Pot Hob 系列由铜和钢组合制成，它们的特别之处在于圆润的“腿部”结构，帮助锅具保持足够高的高度，既能够保证锅具与火焰充分接触，又能避免过度烧伤锅具的精致表面。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213709JBAWqUmz2gtMIboT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.736190\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213709MR9rFgpXqchoPysI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213709sBCSEmur9OJaQKvg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213710InUzHxead30YT2up.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.736190\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018060721371070qleOkvwCRsUFHj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.736190\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213710SETywqPBlsoD2NkY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.736190\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213710GI0CvwrPDRa8dVj3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/06/06/cut-your-dish-use-in-half/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Surreal Table by Analogia Project</h3><p>The Surreal Table 是一个以当代餐桌为探索领域的实验性项目，包括五件动物形状的手工器皿：蜗牛、鸡脚、海豚尾巴、刺猬和公羊。设计师试图带领用户去了解一个古老饮酒仪式的世界。从古希腊时期葡萄酒被呈上餐桌，作为对战胜勇士的奖赏，和对下次战斗的鼓舞，是个荣耀及神圣的象征。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213755jSCHQ348Noh1uc5B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.789731\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213755OTVoAU3hzW42rtDF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.045232\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213755LhxDz48QceZC9XUl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806072137566KYncViXLla0gtWI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.756724\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213756jKEhOgoD57RxPruT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.984108\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213756kr7g0RWCVlTn8MvU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647922\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213756eKvRjpr6sMVf5mnS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://analogiaproject.com/#/rhyton/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Analogia Project</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>58-piece Makeup Line by Crayola &amp; ASOS</h3><p>蜡笔品牌 Crayola 与时尚品牌 ASOS 推出了独家化妆品系列。过去 Crayola 推出过很多联名系列，不过是以蜡笔状推出唇膏、眼影，但这次的全新彩妆系列，完全将蜡笔的特质发挥到极致。整个系列有 58 件产品，足足 95 种颜色，种类就有唇脸两用笔、睫毛膏、眼影等等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213839BLNvmuaOdF873Pb2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.276284\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213839zD0tR2krdxEjiAuC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213839o4rzFxtB1ONcGqSD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.276284\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213840Qw0tDUjSsgO8vapm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504890\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213840W0VlDgbNEG9wF8cq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504890\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806072138403W5bxLYrID8ytgua.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504890\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213840P0LOabR4Z3IklAev.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504890\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Laguna by Elena Trevisan for SITIA</h3><p>定制家具品牌 SITIA 推出了针对办公空间和公共休闲空间的新产品。SITIA 每一款产品的特点在于可以根据客户的喜好进行个性化设计。模块化沙发 Laguna 出自设计师 Elena Trevisan 之手，灵感来自 1950 年代的美学风格。Laguna 的模块既有弯曲形状，也有笔直结构的，纤细的腿部结构也是其醒目的标志之一。当把它们组合在一起时，可塑性极高，适用的场合也更广泛。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806072139121JNkCd4QHY0rWOGV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639062\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213912aLZbv4cyYrlNQ2US.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213912QGvzkuf073KrnegL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.717187\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213913kd4WfhlG1PMuweRp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213913swyNpr96TEIfF34A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607213913k3MvlQSzmsR9dgcj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.573438\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.sitia.com/en/products/sofas/laguna\" rel=\"nofollow\">SITIA</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Hone by Christopher Sarkisian</h3><p>设计师 Christopher Sarkisian 推出的这款名为 Hone 的多功能台灯，意在让用户专注于自己的工作。设计师表示，如今智能手机太容易让人们分散注意力，但 Hone 台灯的基座暗藏玄机，它不仅仅是一个无线充电底座，也是一个可以设置的触发器，按照用户的设置，手机在放入基座上时会迅速转换为“请勿打扰”模式。</p><p>与其复杂的功能相比，Hone 的结构却尽可能得简单利落，也很适合作为床头灯使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806072140084CjQ5LVchpO3st27.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607214008ud2RVFlw5QCONjZ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607214008xktoDFclWnIAGjEH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607214009I6KaJ57h4ocYgz8Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607214009Yq4JcdOPf5XuziIk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806072140091aBWJYkIwOuxATyX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180607214009Amjdu4kFIQL0f7Vc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/66218121/Hone\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}